00:05:52,204 --> 00:05:53,204
I wonder what happened.

118
00:05:53,304 --> 00:05:54,537
PINION: What a complete idiot.

119
00:05:54,637 --> 00:05:57,704
We should just toss him
overboard and be-- geh!

120
00:05:57,804 --> 00:05:59,104
AMY: Don't be rude.

121
