become productive adults?

138
00:06:37,470 --> 00:06:38,904
CHAMBER: Requesting next order.

139
00:06:39,004 --> 00:06:39,470
-Yea.

140
00:06:39,570 --> 00:06:40,704
Hold on a sec.

141
