143
00:06:43,004 --> 00:06:44,504
CHILD 3: Say something.

144
00:06:44,604 --> 00:06:45,904
CHILD 4: Show us how you fly.

145
00:06:46,004 --> 00:06:48,337
CHAMBER: Obstructions
prevent completion of duties.

146
00:06:48,437 --> 00:06:50,437
