you don't hurt anybody.

149
00:06:54,037 --> 00:06:54,537
CHAMBER: Roger.

150
00:06:58,570 --> 00:06:59,470
-Ledo.

151
00:06:59,570 --> 00:07:01,304
How are you doing?

152
00:07:01,404 --> 00:07:03,004
-I'm on standby.

153
00:07:03,104 --> 00:07:04,070
-You're what?

154
00:07:04,170 --> 00:07:04,604
Oh.

155
00:07:04,704 --> 00:07:07,137
Standing by.

156
00:07:07,237 --> 00:07:08,237
What's that in your hand?

157
00:07:08,337 --> 00:07:08,904
Did you make it?

158
00:07:09,004 --> 00:07:10,404
What is it?

159
00:07:10,504 --> 00:07:12,104
LEDO: I don't know

160
00:07:12,204 --> 00:07:14,870
-You're making it but you
don't know what it is?

161
00:07:14,970 --> 00:07:16,404
That's usual.

162
00:07:16,504 --> 00:07:18,270
Your material's strange too.

163
00:07:18,370 --> 00:07:21,137
--[non-english speech]
Not here on earth.

164
00:07:24,504 --> 00:07:26,937
-It's beautiful.

165
00:07:27,037 --> 00:07:28,804
-If Amy wants, I give.

166
00:07:28,904 --> 00:07:29,370
-Really?

167
00:07:29,470 --> 00:07:29,970
Are you sure?

168
00:07:35,237 --> 00:07:36,137
Hey.

169
00:07:36,237 --> 00:07:37,137
Why don't we walk
around for a bit.

170
00:07:40,970 --> 00:07:43,670
This will make a great
gift for my little brother.

171
00:07:43,770 --> 00:07:44,637
LEDO: Little brother?

172
00:07:44,737 --> 00:07:45,537
-Uh-huh.

173
00:07:45,637 --> 00:07:47,270
His name is Bebel.

174
00:07:47,370 --> 00:07:49,804
He's good at working
with his hands.

175
00:07:49,904 --> 00:07:50,904
-[non-english speech]

176
00:07:51,004 --> 00:07:52,737
CHAMBER: Please
define little brother.

177
00:07:52,837 --> 00:07:53,304
-Oh.

178
00:07:53,404 --> 00:07:54,604
Little brother?

179
00:07:54,704 --> 00:07:58,370
That means your sibling,
a younger male sibling.

180
00:07:58,470 --> 00:08:01,137
Like a family member.

181
00:08:01,237 --> 00:08:02,204
LEDO: Fa-mi-ly?

182
00:08:02,304 --> 00:08:03,970
CHAMBER: In ancient
civilization,

183
00:08:04,070 --> 00:08:07,404
family was the label applied
to societal units comprised

184
