-Ledo, you don't have family?

187
00:08:15,870 --> 00:08:17,004
-Inefficient.

188
00:08:17,104 --> 00:08:18,037
Not needed.

189
00:08:18,137 --> 00:08:19,937
-Inefficient?

190
00:08:20,037 --> 00:08:23,204
I gotta say Ledo, it sounds
like where you're from

191
00:08:23,304 --> 00:08:25,737
is pretty rough.

192
