Bebel really wants
to talk to you

193
00:08:27,370 --> 00:08:28,904
and ask you all about space.

194
00:08:29,004 --> 00:08:31,104
LEDO: About space?

195
00:08:31,204 --> 00:08:32,304
AMY: Yeah.

196
00:08:32,404 --> 00:08:34,670
He's very interesting in
the stars and the vehicles

197
00:08:34,770 --> 00:08:36,837
you use to travel up there.

198
00:08:36,937 --> 00:08:38,304
He's a smart kid.

199
00:08:38,404 --> 00:08:40,737
It's just that his body
is weak so he can't just

200
00:08:40,837 --> 00:08:42,670
walk around whenever
he wants to.

201
00:08:42,770 --> 00:08:44,504
LEDO: Body is weak?

202
00:08:44,604 --> 00:08:46,170
-It's in his chest.

203
00:08:46,270 --> 00:08:48,704
He's got a disease or something.

204
00:08:48,804 --> 00:08:49,770
LEDO: [non-english speech]

205
00:08:49,870 --> 00:08:51,204
CHAMBER: In the
Galactic Alliance,

