00:09:09,570 --> 00:09:11,204
CHAMBER: Is there
another with information

214
00:09:11,304 --> 00:09:13,704
that I might converse
with to learn more?

215
00:09:13,804 --> 00:09:16,204
-Learn more?

216
00:09:16,304 --> 00:09:18,770
In that case why don't I take
you to meet Doctor Oldham.

217
00:09:18,870 --> 00:09:20,837
-Oldham?

218
00:09:20,937 --> 00:09:24,837
-He's a medical doctor but
people all him the sage.

219
00:09:24,937 --> 00:09:26,737
He's the smartest person
in all of Gargantia.

220
00:09:41,137 --> 00:09:42,170
Over here.

221
00:09:42,270 --> 00:09:44,137
-[grunt]

222
00:09:51,004 --> 00:09:51,770
-Hello.

223
00:09:51,870 --> 00:09:52,637
NURSE: Hi.

224
00:09:52,737 --> 00:09:54,604
-Is Doctor Oldham in?

225
00:09:54,704 --> 00:09:55,604
-Oh, Amy.

226
00:09:55,704 --> 00:09:56,137
Hello.

227
00:09:56,237 --> 00:09:57,104
BOY: Doctor.

228
00:09:57,204 --> 00:09:58,604
Amy's here .

229
00:09:58,704 --> 00:09:59,604
-Hello?

230
00:09:59,704 --> 00:10:00,537
Doctor Oldham.

231
00:10:00,637 --> 00:10:03,637
-Nice to see you Amy.

232
00:10:03,737 --> 00:10:07,104
-I brought someone to meet you.

233
00:10:07,204 --> 00:10:11,270
-If I had to guess,
I'd say you were Ledo.

234
00:10:11,370 --> 00:10:13,970
-He says he's got something
he wants to ask you.

235
00:10:14,070 --> 00:10:15,404
-Oh?

236
00:10:15,504 --> 00:10:18,404
-Well, I've still got work to
do so I'm going to head out.

237
00:10:18,504 --> 00:10:20,770
-You're always so busy Amy.

238
00:10:20,870 --> 00:10:22,637
-Ledo, I'll come back
to pick you up later.

239
00:10:22,737 --> 00:10:23,437
So wait downstairs.

240
00:10:26,137 --> 00:10:29,870
