and understand words.

246
00:10:41,570 --> 00:10:42,937
-Correct.

247
00:10:43,037 --> 00:10:45,237
-Technology lost long ago.

248
00:10:45,337 --> 00:10:49,270
I never imagined I'd ever lay
my eyes on the real thing.

249
00:10:49,370 --> 00:10:51,404
-May I ask question.

250
00:10:51,504 --> 00:10:54,237
-Of course, though I
may not know the answer.

251
00:10:54,337 --> 00:10:54,904
Have a seat.

252
00:10:59,070 --> 00:11:01,004
Now go ahead, ask.

253
00:11:01,104 --> 00:11:02,137
-[non-english speech]

254
00:11:02,237 --> 00:11:03,504
CHAMBER: I would
like to know how

255
00:11:03,604 --> 00:11:05,704
I can return to the
Galactic Alliance.

256
00:11:05,804 --> 00:11:08,337
-I'm afraid I don't possess
any knowledge pertaining

257
00:11:08,437 --> 00:11:09,804
to that subject.

258
00:11:09,904 --> 00:11:12,604
As you can see, the majority
of the ancient wisdom

259
00:11:12,704 --> 00:11:15,537
has been lost to
us for generations.

260
00:11:15,637 --> 00:11:19,270
Information about space
travel is especially scarce.

261
00:11:19,370 --> 00:11:21,137
Currently, this is
the only knowledge

262
00:11:21,237 --> 00:11:24,670
of the heavens that
remains and was left to us.

263
00:11:24,770 --> 00:11:28,170
Sadly, I doubt this is
what you're looking for.

264
00:11:28,270 --> 00:11:31,070
I'm sorry I don't
have anything more.

265
00:11:31,170 --> 00:11:34,437
-Can't be helped.

266
00:11:34,537 --> 00:11:37,704
May I ask you one more question?

267
00:11:37,804 --> 00:11:39,404
-Yes, ask all you want.

268
00:11:39,504 --> 00:11:40,404
-[non-english speech]

269
00:11:40,504 --> 00:11:41,837
CHAMBER: I would
like your explanation

